# Environment (use Docker env vars instead)
# =====================
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# =====================
# Development files
# =====================
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output

# =====================
# IDE / Editor
# =====================
**/.idea
**/.vscode
**/*.swp
**/*.swo

# =====================
# OS Files
# =====================
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# =====================
# Documentation & Assets (not needed in container)
# =====================
*.md
!README.md
assets/
docs/

